---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
import { SITE, WHATSAPP_LINK } from '../config';

const title = 'About Subbaraju Brokerage | Agri Commodity Brokers, Challakere';
const description =
  'About Subbaraju Brokerage — an agricultural commodity brokerage based in Challakere, Chitradurga district, Karnataka. Local market knowledge, verified network, honest dealing.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pt-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-ink/60">
      <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a> › <span>About</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-forest-800">
      About Subbaraju Brokerage
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink/85">
      Subbaraju Brokerage is an agricultural commodity brokerage based in
      <strong>Challakere, Chitradurga district, Karnataka</strong>. We connect the people who grow,
      mill and manufacture agri commodities with the people who buy, distribute and retail them —
      across Karnataka and into neighbouring states.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-forest-700">Why Challakere</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-ink/85">
      Challakere is one of central Karnataka’s most important agricultural trading towns. Its
      market yard has been a hub for the groundnut trade for generations — the town is often
      called the region’s “oil city” — and the surrounding dryland belt produces maize, ragi,
      pulses and more. Sitting on the highway between Bengaluru and North Karnataka, Challakere
      is a natural meeting point between the growing belts and the consuming markets.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-ink/85">
      Being physically present in this market matters. Rates in agri trade change daily —
      sometimes hourly — and a broker who walks the yard, sees the arrivals and talks to the
      traders knows the real price, not the rumoured one. That is the knowledge we put to work
      for every client.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-forest-700">Our Experience</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-ink/85">
      Our family has been part of the Challakere commodity trade for years. In that time we have
      built working relationships with rice mills, dal mills, roasting units, feed plants,
      wholesale merchants and transporters across Karnataka. Those relationships are the real
      asset a broker offers: when you post a requirement with us, it goes to people we know will
      perform — lift on time, deliver the agreed grade, and pay as promised.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-forest-700">How We Think About Trust</h2>
    <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-forest-600/10 bg-cream-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-forest-700">Describe lots honestly</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-ink/80">
          Moisture, mixing, grade — a lot is described exactly as it is. A buyer surprised at
          unloading is a buyer lost forever, and we intend to trade with the same people for
          decades.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-forest-600/10 bg-cream-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-forest-700">Fix everything up front</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-ink/80">
          Rate, brokerage, weighment terms, payment schedule — all agreed before the lorry is
          loaded. No deductions invented later, on either side.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-forest-600/10 bg-cream-50 p-5">
        <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-forest-700">Stay until it is settled</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-ink/80">
          Our involvement doesn’t end when the deal is fixed. We track dispatch, delivery and
          payment, and we pick up the phone when you call.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-forest-700">Where We Operate</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-ink/85">
      We are based in Challakere and serve buyers and sellers across the whole of
      <strong>Karnataka, Andhra Pradesh and Tamil Nadu</strong> — from the mandis of central
      Karnataka to feed mills, processors and wholesale markets in all three states. We speak
      Kannada, English, Hindi and Telugu, so language is never a barrier to a deal.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-8 rounded-2xl bg-forest-100/60 p-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-forest-800">
      The simplest way to judge a broker is to do one deal. Call us at
      <a href={`tel:${SITE.phoneRaw}`} class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-4">{SITE.phoneDisplay}</a>,
      <a href={WHATSAPP_LINK} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-4">WhatsApp us</a>,
      or <a href="/contact/" class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-4">post your requirement</a> —
      and see how we work.
    </p>
  </section>

  <CtaBand />
</Layout>
